{"tid":1753111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強某程度幫左我地","createTime":"2019-11-25T01:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T02:34:03.000Z","uid":191926,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6bad5a92cdad1d62e768c775de3484395abab0a8","tid":1753111,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"呢2星期黑警<br />\n戰術上輕微成功  戰略上失敗<br />\n<br />\n其實黎明行動  <br />\n後期果幾日  <br />\n已經變成左 以前的塞鐵行動<br />\n<br />\n人民鬥人民的問題好嚴重<br />\n結果令民意出現左輕微逆轉<br />\n<br />\n如果鄧炳強無錯誤<br />\n發動中大，理大兩役<br />\n<br />\n1.美國國會內部支持人權法案聲音<br />\n唔會急劇升溫<br />\n<br />\n本來麥康奈爾 佢已經穩住左美國內部<br />\n所以2星期前風向係最快都要明年初......<br />\n<br />\n2. 黎明活動的民意逆轉效果加大<br />\n<br />\n如果佢放軟手腳<br />\n縱容2星期 黎明活動 用人民鬥人民<br />\n民意逆轉會更嚴重<br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n理大好多勇武派最後都係走到  <br />\n無法全殲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c28e8378532d6ceeea473fce37e18a5f5d5a456","tid":1753111,"uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/jZg2Jy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FjZg2Jy.gif&h=9b3ca869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fffbb0bbe6db03a6bb0f46b5bd152e7424763f8a","tid":1753111,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:31:41.000Z","msg":"傻強:咪撚講啦屌!"},{"pid":"22ab56600cc402ed8261a7fef181900d55238583","tid":1753111,"uid":221650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:36:40.000Z","msg":"神級豬隊友"},{"pid":"5ac4686ff87ebcbc92189277ba8e467e31f65dba","tid":1753111,"uid":65074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"功勞要歸於理大手足決定留守<br />\n留守嘅意志係一種statement<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強有d似林鄭路線  好打得但唔知自己打緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156c558cd86f4da4db4271f3534d30c389e9534f","tid":1753111,"uid":25055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ac4686ff87ebcbc92189277ba